'''Galactic Weekly NewsStack''' was an anti-[[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] news agency that operated during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. It was a major thorn in [[Commission for the Preservation of the New Order/Legends|COMPNOR's]] side; Imperial forces had been working very hard in order to stop this agency from broadcasting. Galactic Weekly NewsStack's [[Virastack|programs]] acted like a virus program, entering [[HoloNet/Legends|HoloNet]] systems and the networks of larger corporations. COMPNOR, however, had no success in tracing the true origin of the agency. The only thing that they were able to find was that it was originally transmitted from somewhere in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] by an editor who called himself [[Palpatine II]].

